CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper March 2, 1946, pg. 13, reads: "Homecoming - Lieut. Edward M. Plummer Jr., former Allegheny Valley correspondent for the Pittsburgh Courier, poses with Mrs. Plummer, a Californian on a visit here.  They enjoyed many social courtesies during their stay in the Smoky City. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Mrs. Plummer and Lieut. Edward M. Plummer Jr. seated in front of dark curtain in Harris Studio
